Test Case 1: Login form_positive test
Precondition: Start page of browser is opened, internet connection is set up.
Steps:
    1. Open link 'http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login'
    2. Fill in "student" in email form.
    3. Fill in "909090" in password form.
    4. Click "Вход" button.
Expected Result: Main page is opened
Post Condition: Click "Студент" -> "Выход". Close the browser.

________________

Test Case 2: Register form_positive test
Precondition: Start page of browser is opened, internet connection is set up.
Steps:
    1. Open link 'http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login'
    2. Click "Зарегистрироваться" button.
Expected Result: Register page is opened
Post Condition: Close the browser.

________________

Test Case 3: Party Transactions_Creation with empty fields_negative test
Precondition: Start page of browser is opened, internet connection is set up.
Steps:
    1. Open link 'http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login'
    2. Click on "Словари" area -> Select "Стороны сделок" .
    3. Click "Add"(+) button.
    4. In newly opened window leave all fields empty and click "Создать"
Expected Result: Validation message is displayed : "Заполните это поле". Any new Party Transaction with empty fields is not saved.
Post Condition: Click "Студент" -> "Выход". Close the browser.

________________

Test Case 4: Deals_Add and Delete_positive test
Precondition: Start page of browser is opened, internet connection is set up.
Steps:
    1. Open link 'http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login'
    2. Click on "Сделки" tab.
    3. Click "Add"(+) button.
    4. In newly opened window input:
        "Deal date" section includes 5 drop-downs, select following in each:
            Day - 08
            Month - "марта"
            Year - 2017
            Hour - leave default value
            Minutes - leave default value
        "Тип сделки" - 'обмен'
        "Покупатель" - 'ОАО "МММ"'
        "Поставщик" - 'ЧП "Рога и Копыта"'
    5. Click "Создать". New row is added to the list.
    6. Click on newly added row.
    7. Click "Удалить".
Expected Result: The row is deleted from the list of Deals.
Post Condition: Click "Студент" -> "Выход". Close the browser.



